Example
Close a ZIP directory entry opened by zip_entry_open():
<?php
$zip = zip_open("test.zip");
if ($zip) {
while ($zip_entry = zip_read($zip)) {
if (zip_entry_open($zip, $zip_entry)) {
// some code
// Close directory entry
zip_entry_close($zip_entry);
}
}
zip_close($zip);
}
?>
Definition and Usage
The zip_entry_close() function closes a ZIP directory entry opened by zip_entry_open().
Syntax
zip_entry_close(
zip_entry
)
Parameter Values
Parameter
Description
zip_entry
Required. Specifies the ZIP directory entry returned by zip_read()
Technical Details
Return Value:
TRUE on success. FALSE on failure
PHP Version:
4.1.0+

